								    Apagado em:			<fmt:formatDate value="${ pro.deleted_at }" pattern="dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm"/></small>
									<!--									  (3) ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^	-->
	                      	  	</td>
	                      	  	
	                      	  	<td>
					              	<button type="button"							 data-id="${ pro.id_produto }"
